reviews.review_text: Lost sailor Great tune along w/circumstance.I missed this show did not get on the bus Villa few months later. Ended up seeing 95 or so shows up until 90. After Brent it was hard for me to open up for awhile. Eventually I did check out shows with Vince and Bruce and oh boy Mayer on the wolf will blow the socks off.but thanks again Matt, you are a hero for doing the work to put these memories on the Inter web. Peace people. We will all meet again some day, well most of us. Stay on the bus. Further.
